<article class="text-default relative z-10 w-full p-8 lg:p-12 max-w-[65ch] mx-auto tracking-[0.0125em] linkify text-pretty">

	<h1 class="spacer-t spacer-b-md font-bold tracking-[-0.0125em] text-white text-heading-xl">
		Website Hosting
	</h1>

	<div class="details space-y-8 spacer-b-md">
		<p>I provide website hosting as part of the <a href="{{ '/info/maintenance/' | url }}">maintenance package</a>, or as a standalone service for static websites that don't require a CMS.</p>

		<p>Websites are hosted on dedicated, secure servers in a London datacentre, chosen for their reliability, performance, and security. UK-based hosting also means your website data stays within the UK, which can help with data compliance.</p>

		<h2 class="font-bold tracking-[-0.0125em] text-white text-heading spacer-t-xs">What's Included</h2>

		<p>Whether hosting is part of your maintenance plan or a standalone arrangement, the following is included:</p>

		<div class="space-y-6">
			<dl>
				<dt class="font-semibold text-white/90 block">SSL Certificate</dt>
				<dd>Your website is secured with an SSL certificate, keeping data encrypted and your site trusted by browsers.</dd>
			</dl>

			<dl>
				<dt class="font-semibold text-white/90 block">Uptime Monitoring</dt>
				<dd>I monitor your website minute by minute and proactively investigate any issues that arise.</dd>
			</dl>

			<dl>
				<dt class="font-semibold text-white/90 block">Server Updates</dt>
				<dd>The server your website runs on is regularly updated and optimised for performance and security.</dd>
			</dl>

			<dl class="space-y-2">
				<dt class="font-semibold text-white/90 block">Backups</dt>
				<dd>Your website files and database are backed up daily and stored in multiple secure locations.</dd>

				<dd><em class="opacity-75 text-lg">Please note: while every effort is made to maintain reliable backups, I recommend keeping your own copies of any critical content or data. Backups are provided as a precautionary measure and complete recovery cannot be guaranteed in all scenarios.</em></dd>
			</dl>
		</div>

		<h2 class="font-bold tracking-[-0.0125em] text-white text-heading spacer-t-xs">Prefer to Manage Your Own Hosting?</h2>

		<p>That's absolutely fine. If you'd rather handle hosting yourself, I'm happy to recommend reputable shared hosting providers that offer a good balance of performance, support, and value.</p>

		<p>If you have any questions, feel free to get in touch at <a href="mailto:ryan@yep.digital">ryan@yep.digital</a>.</p>

